    "media_id": "89087220816439253",
    "parent_id": "10000000001",
    "text": "Margaux. The light in this is exactly right — feels like Fishtown at 7am before anyone's awake.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:54:58+00:00",
    "user_id": "28351631961927271",
    "username": "margaux"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "79206385768729074",
    "like_count": "3",
    "media_id": "59933649191522537",
    "parent_id": "10000000002",
    "text": "Theo. This light is exactly what I've been chasing in the studio. Where was this?",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-09T00:47:33+00:00",
    "user_id": "58143422689031186",
    "username": "theo"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "70312023172952845",
    "like_count": "6",
    "media_id": "55893147793157666",
    "parent_id": "10000000003",
    "text": "Kim — that photo from Saturday's opening caught something I didn't expect. The light near Theo's piece was doing real wo",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-08T14:40:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "21785057039063970",
    "username": "kim"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "62987134855467866",
    "like_count": "9",
    "media_id": "80146634502870490",
    "parent_id": "10000000004",
    "text": "Sent this to Kim — she said it's the most Philly thing she's ever seen. That's either a compliment or a warning.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-07T10:35:21+00:00",
    "user_id": "25977738784972977",
    "username": "devon"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "20830542842223342",
    "like_count": "10",
    "media_id": "19583656139816890",
    "parent_id": "10000000005",
    "text": "Sent you the Fishtown series from this morning's walk. The light on Frankford Ave was actually doing something.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-06T08:46:46+00:00",
    "user_id": "88917930903877904",
    "username": "ruth"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "75583549292097857",
    "like_count": "19",
    "media_id": "35380084574541132",
    "parent_id": "10000000006",
    "text": "Sam, did you catch Theo's installation shot? Looks like it belongs in a Fishtown alley. Genuinely strange work.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-07T19:01:21+00:00",
    "user_id": "20836269298160091",
    "username": "sam"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "58594671269397873",
    "like_count": "4",
    "media_id": "89262006009589286",
    "parent_id": "10000000007",
    "text": "Nina — caught Kim's install shots from the Fishtown show. The light in that third frame is everything.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-09T04:23:37+00:00",
    "user_id": "79238919239299809",
    "username": "nina"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "63096108393584272",
    "like_count": "22",
    "media_id": "79285307975062816",
    "parent_id": "10000000008",
    "text": "Franklin — printed the riverfront shot from Tuesday's walk. Framing it for the studio.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-07T23:02:35+00:00",
    "user_id": "33360612708575604",
    "username": "franklin"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "34429768569853330",
    "like_count": "17",
    "media_id": "98466777185998752",
    "parent_id": "10000000009",
    "text": "Anh, saw the photo — that light in the shot is doing something. Reminds me of the work I've been prepping for Kim's spri",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-08T10:22:19+00:00",
    "user_id": "35515686886763806",
    "username": "anh"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "15362706522347051",
    "like_count": "11",
    "media_id": "13012085980069516",
    "parent_id": "10000000010",
    "text": "Carol — took your advice and went outside for the afternoon light. Fishtown, golden hour. Margaux got this shot of me.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-02T23:27:59+00:00",
    "user_id": "67579715808025804",
    "username": "carol"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "27945491449558518",
    "like_count": "2",
    "media_id": "55234477292315543",
    "parent_id": "10000000011",
    "text": "The light in that shot is exactly what I described to Kim last month. Philadelphia does grey better than anywhere.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-05T21:59:06+00:00",
    "user_id": "30997498896103472",
    "username": "dana"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "27132309289052074",
    "like_count": "21",
    "media_id": "34477218123610516",
    "parent_id": "10000000012",
    "text": "Showed this to Kim last week — she wants to know if there's a series. I think she's right.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-02T09:53:39+00:00",
    "user_id": "39521517958090244",
    "username": "marisol"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "70853661898899971",
    "like_count": "8",
    "media_id": "14576373998869098",
    "parent_id": "10000000013",
    "text": "Showed Kim the riverfront shots from Tuesday — she wants the triptych for the October show.",
    "timestamp": "2025-11-04T02:41:45+00:00",
    "user_id": "90489274603883474",
    "username": "margaret"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "75356561834908921",
    "like_count": "10",
    "media_id": "87177740439870724",
    "parent_id": "10000000014",
    "text": "Saw the photo from last semester's critique wall. Harrington finally got good lighting in that space.",
    "timestamp": "2025-10-30T04:14:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "81262977410240748",
    "username": "sarah"
  },
  {
    "hidden": "false",
    "id": "31606606405220481",
    "like_count": "2",
    "media_id": "76871014767853202",
    "parent_id": "10000000015",
    "text": "Owen — pulled this up during my studio block. Spare, like Margaux would say. Keep it.",
    "timestamp": "2025-10-28T02:47:44+00:00",
    "user_id": "47218820752309014",
    "username": "owen"
  }
]